Class CovidGraphSpread

  • java.lang.Object
    • git.CovidGraphSpread

  • public class CovidGraphSpread
extends java.lang.Object
    The CovidGraphSpread will be used to retrieve all information from the repository This class connects to Git, Accesses the covid19spreading.rdf file available in the repository, Retrieves all covid19spreading.rdf file versions that have tags associated, and builds a html table.
